    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it a great choice for a daily driver. While the exterior paint retains a nice shine, there are a few minor rock chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. The interior is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics and features are fully functional, and it has a solid service history.",
