      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is honestly in such incredible shape, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no scuffs\u2014just pure perfection inside and out. I'm really sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Come take a look and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
