    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, a specimen of uncompromising mechanical integrity. This vehicle is powered by the high-revving F22C1 inline-four, featuring a factory-spec valvetrain and seamless VTEC engagement. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a double-wishbone suspension that retains its original damping characteristics and surgical turn-in precision. All body panels carry matching VIN tags, confirming a preserved, factory-original state. With no modifications and perfect synchro engagement, this S2000 offers the definitive analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
